<plot>This Sportscope short shows youngsters (8 years old and up) training at the Junior Bengal Lancers riding school in Halifax. Later they demonstrate their skills at a celebration in Annapolis, Nova Scotia. Six-year-old 'Heather Cameron (II)' (qv), who is too young to be a student, is named official mascot of the unit.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?092513</url></doc>
